address: Retreat (6900 East Green Lake Way N)
description:
it's the 4th monday of the month, which means a field trip! come get in some monday miles starting from retreat for a classic green lake loop*. those looking to wrap up their runs earlier can call it at the loop, or add on another 3 miles through ravenna! make sure to bring headlamps for the Big Dark. stick around afterwards to grab a dinner, treat, and/or bevvy from retreat. 

*our route will pass by the green lake community center ballot drop box for those needing to hand in their ballots. be cute and vote!!!

~ this no-drop run is open to women, non-binary, and trans people who are comfortable in a space that centers the experiences of women. our only rule is that nobody runs alone :) ~
title: womxn run the herd | retreat field trip

description:
join us for some early morning urban trail miles! our route starts from fuel coffee in montlake and goes through the arb and interlaken to cover 5 miles and 400' of vert. make sure to bring a headlamp! stick around after for coffee from fuel. our only rule is that no one runs alone :) 

~ this no-drop, bi-weekly tuesday morning run is open to women, non-binary, and trans people who are comfortable in a space that centers the experiences of women ~
title: wrth | morning edition
